Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:05.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猪猪一个人去地学奥林匹克了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:09.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  这周星期天好像会进行预选
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:14.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真令人吃惊  那孩子竟然会接受这样的挑战…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:18.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的呢  我也想去参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:21.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,四年一次太难得了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.58,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1289.371,906.571)}矿苗攀岩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:24.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地学奥林匹克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:26.79,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636.572,491.714)}化石开掘竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,都有些什么竞赛项目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.80,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1242.971,817.514)}望远镜\N寻星竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:29.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,竞赛…不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:32.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:35.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为叫奥林匹克我还以为一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在意的话就先去调查下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.44,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&HFF&\fs70\move(939.2,408.6,939.2,1131.8)}日本地学奥林匹克募集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:45.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地学奥林匹克是指  面向初高中生的地学知识竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:46.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,每年都会举办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:50.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,从通过了国内预选和终选的学生中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:53.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,挑选出去参加国际大赛的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:56.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樱学姐  知道得真详细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:58.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我家妹妹也会去参加
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:00.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:02.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樱学姐原来有妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,现在读初三
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:06.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,中学生就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:08.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说是在突破了预选和终选后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:11.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想去参加在泰国举办的国际大赛来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:13.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,泰国…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1119.543,147.257)}想要的土特产清单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1226.552,312.82)}泰式酸辣汤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1177.79,442.648)}泰式咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1046.362,535.447)}大象周边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024.152,683.79)}泰拳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:17.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈米菈  太性急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:20.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但话说回来猪猪为什么突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看了合宿时候的照片  一下子就来劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:28.35,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,{\frz353.5\fs30\pos(749.667,237.111)}日本地学奥林匹克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:28.35,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,{\frz353.5\fs30\pos(769.667,267.667)}过去在鉴定试验中使用过的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:28.35,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,{\frz353.5\fs30\pos(766.778,294.333)}岩石·矿物·化石标本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:28.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来如此  是地质标本馆里的展示呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:30.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我以前觉得对我们这样的小社团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:34.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那完全是另一个世界的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:36.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,然而那孩子却…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:40.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:45.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樱学姐  刚刚的表情变得超温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,明明是在表扬她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:51.45,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,===op===
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.39,Asteroid - title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1100,1100)\blur15\pos(586.133,917.466)}冬天的钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这儿  以前一定是条河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,探险是之后的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今天的我  是地学部的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱着强韧的心情  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.79,Asteroid - SongTi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1282.667,534)}日本地学奥林匹克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.79,Asteroid - SongTi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(838.667,507.333)}考试会场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好  好慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来有这么多人参加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,而且净是些不认识的学校的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,邻座的同学  今天多多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你还挺有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是冴木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是猪濑  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:16.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小猪濑在紧张吗  第一次参加？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:21.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  我们学校就只有我一人参加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:25.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,而且只要一想到在场的大家都是竞争对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就有一种疏远的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:28.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对手？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我去年一路走到了终试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,当然  也是抱着不会输给其他人的心情参加的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但转念一想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:46.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家都是些对地学有着莫大兴趣的同类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,再说  大会的结果可以用于一些大学的入学申请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以这个为目标的人当然也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有这种制度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,报名表上写着的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对梦露学姐暂且保密好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.78,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1400,388.667)}考试开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.78,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1397.334,510)}考试结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.78,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1709.333,676.667)}11:30以后\N可以交卷离开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,差不多了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,总之  愉快地去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:09.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小猪濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,现在开始下发试卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太厉害了  冴木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,竟然是备选经验者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:24.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一定是个头脑非常聪明  解题速度也很快的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是发现了猎物的野兽的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,集中集中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,首先是地质学科的题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地质罗盘磁针的读法  叠覆律  指准化石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这部分问题解起来好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地质剖面图  火山  岩浆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,气象学科  海洋学科  环境学科…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是我不擅长学科的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然也大致学习过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:05.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但果然没有理解到原理的话感觉解不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,最后是  天文学科
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是小行星的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,咦  比起想象中解起来轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,毕竟一直都和她们待在社团活动室里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还有十分钟结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:31.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么办…还有一道题怎么都搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,做得快的人都已经离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:38.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,从A到O中选出两段正确的描述
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:43.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,从A到O…从A到O…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,从A到O？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,AO！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:51.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,/注：蓝的名字发音是AO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,结束了结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小猪濑也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:05.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,脑子里塞满的知识一下全放空了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是  来参加真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,来到这里第一次感觉到的东西有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:21.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比如自己是多么渺小之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:27.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  觉得世界比自己想象的还要宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我还以为是在说身高的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,机会难得  一起走到车站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:34.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对了  我在回去路上有件事情想做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:41.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为我在河流填上的地方发现好像有一条新的小道出现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就想去探探险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是什么  好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,结果已经出了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:58.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没有  我自己算了下分很凄惨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是  学姐看上去似乎很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:08.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  我知道了在这个地学部之外也有很多的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:09.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:11.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要看照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要看要看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:18.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,踏出了一步  变得比我们更成熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:21.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要回去了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看到了大家的样子后打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我也得再加把劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这就是冴木同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是回程途中探险时的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,用了数码相机却没有晃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这张是冴木同学拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我拍的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,电磁炉么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为找远藤老师借炉子被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我就从新屋老师那儿借来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就赶紧准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,文化社团的电闸是共用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什么  黑暗火锅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没  是圣诞节年终晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可以的话一起参加如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,承蒙好意  但是新闻部也在举行年终晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以才这个打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:35.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐  以及新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,被训了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这就有点棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:42.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为漏风很严重暖气也不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对了  如果是石烧锅的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石烧锅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:52.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,把高温的石头投入进去烹饪的乡土料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:10:00.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去找作为石头的英安质熔结凝灰岩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:01.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去哪儿找？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,到男鹿半岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也找蓝商量一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.80,Asteroid - Chat4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1340,155)\fad(400,0)}跳闸纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,电磁炉和暖气好像不能同时使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:29.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不开暖气  作为代替给学姐们准备几条毛毯之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,然后再把火锅做辣  让身体暖和起来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.86,Asteroid - Chat4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(1341.333,147.334)\c&H5C6384&\3c&H8BCD84&}鳞片从眼睛里掉出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.65,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：「鳞片从眼睛里掉出来」有令人眼前一亮，恍然大悟的意思，源自圣经故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:43.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的是  我一直都在从米菈那儿获得活力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是能有什么作为回礼就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.51,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\frz6.364\pos(1032,722)}圣诞节\N\N\N{\c&H82B49A&}年终晚会！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:11:00.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,第一回  地学部年终圣诞派对  开始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没想到还能在活动室里吃上火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我说  这金闪闪的究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈借给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在人造卫星上也有用到的隔热毯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在JAXA参观学习的时候买的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,确实买了各种各样的东西呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,围上这个后  感觉就像变成了人造卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是什么感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是这个看上去很暖和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,火锅的味道没问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:40.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小米菈  这个火锅好辣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:44.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只是用了超市里卖的泡菜汤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:46.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:47.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:49.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,难道说是因为这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:55.90,Asteroid - Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,614)}辣椒粉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,追加辣味的辣椒粉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,难道说！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:12:00.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米  米菈说把所有食材都放进去  我就以为…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学姐  稍微等一下再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:05.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,味道挺刺激的还挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:12.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这难道就是大人的味觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  你拜托我要的屋顶顶上的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:19.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,屋顶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想着等大家身子暖和起来了就去看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.85,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,泡菜火锅  真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好  好辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说好的大人的味觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哇  视野好宽阔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:43.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为今天很冷  所以夜空很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就是冬日钻石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:49.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,天狼星  参宿七  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,毕宿五  五车二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:53.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,北河三  南河三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樱学姐你是查阅过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:13:00.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只是因为石头里也有这些名字所以就不知不觉记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:01.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你在笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:06.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对了  在其中加入猎户座的参宿四的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看起来就是大写的G
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你说的Ｇ是英文字母的G吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  连接那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:20.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  原本是地质研的我居然也会仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对于合并还是觉得不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是这样想的话就不会做这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:31.97,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,大家过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是我们送给大家的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可以打开哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是相册！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我拿出了我的偷拍藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,然后麻烦小樱编辑整理成相册了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,社团活动的场景还有活动时的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,居然拍了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有好多照片要是放上去了就显得你们太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,挑选的时候真是费了好大力气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  感觉特别开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:39.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:40.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,泡菜的功效也过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,锅里加点水做乌冬面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,到了这个年纪真是受不了寒冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真亏你们能穿那么短的裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,暖气  暖气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老师  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:05.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:13.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,即使过了三号  来参拜的人还是很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猪猪学姐  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:16.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地图
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说的也是  不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:20.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,两张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这附近修建有规模庞大的治水工程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所有很想和以前的地图对照一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:33.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是治水工程的纪念碑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,来拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学姐  不如我们先去参拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说起来是啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:45.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,参拜完后抽签再去茶屋吃团子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我还想喝甜米酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:50.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是天然石的抽签
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我好想抽一发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,从这里好像看得不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:03.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,从颜色来看好像是水晶  玛瑙  红碧玉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:55.60,Asteroid - Screen8,,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,132.667)}天然石抽签
